sequenceDiagram
    actor Patient as Paciente
    participant UI as Frontend Paciente
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant TRIAGE as Triage Module
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant VDB as Vector Store
    participant LLM as LLM

    Patient->>UI: Registra sintomas y contexto
    UI->>API: POST /consultations
    API-->>UI: Consulta creada
    UI->>API: POST /consultations/{id}/triage
    API->>TRIAGE: Ejecutar flujo de triage
    TRIAGE->>RAG: Solicitar recomendacion fundamentada
    RAG->>VDB: Buscar evidencia relevante
    VDB-->>RAG: Fragmentos y fuentes
    RAG->>LLM: Prompt con contexto clinico
    LLM-->>RAG: Recomendacion estructurada
    RAG-->>TRIAGE: Severidad, recomendacion, fuentes
    TRIAGE-->>API: Resultado consolidado
    API-->>UI: Resultado y decision final
